Dialogue: 1,0:02:10.29,0:02:16.50,Default,,0,0,995,,{\fnConstantia\fs60\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HFAD30F&\4c&HEDE711&}只要你我永遠一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.89,0:02:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,令次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.42,0:02:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,少年為什麼會變成 Hand Shakers 呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.35,0:02:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,沒遵守約定是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,少年的能力沒被奪走的理由   你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.00,0:02:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因為我相信你會遵守提議的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.38,0:02:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.55,0:02:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我們約定好不會讓他成為 Hand Shakers
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.99,0:02:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,你卻沒做到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.47,0:02:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊   我選擇讓那傢伙戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.00,0:02:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這盒子比你想像中還要糟糕還要壞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.12,0:02:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,那少年是沒辦法承受的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.61,0:02:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我要毀掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.96,0:03:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,今天只是來打招呼   等會我還有工作要完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.05,0:03:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,文幸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.44,0:03:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是那傢伙的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是他想做的事我不會有意見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.59,0:03:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,如果是他發自內心決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.12,0:03:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,即使是與人戰鬥我也會認同
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的是我才對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.85,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,是文文的錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.48,0:03:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,擁有那樣的能力很不好我們應該非常清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,往這裡   潔西卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,潔西卡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,潔西卡！！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,潔西卡…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,就是不願意重蹈覆轍
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因此才拜託令次接受這個提案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,然而這就是結果嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.72,0:04:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你的決心是這麼容易動搖的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,My man
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.27,0:04:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,手綱先生一定願意借給我力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,可是遙會被奧池帶走都是因為我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.86,0:04:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你在那裡猶豫什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你以為我沒有察覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:04:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,父母知道的比你想像的還多
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,媽媽也是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.29,0:04:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.11,Default,,0,0,0,,要聯絡手綱嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.63,0:05:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,肯定發生事情了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你從回來就是那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,您知道奧池集團嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.02,0:05:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啊   是個大企業嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.79,0:05:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,就算沒有直接接觸   工作多少也有關聯…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.96,0:05:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,謠傳他們干預 Hand Shakers  是真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.68,0:05:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,他們提出想借用我的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,說是我「寧錄」的能力很特別
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.30,0:05:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(871.333,981.333)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你接受了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不過遙卻被他們帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.88,0:05:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,小遙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.04,0:05:46.69,Default,,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.86,0:05:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.64,0:05:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,似乎不是被強迫的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也許是遙自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.06,0:05:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你想怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做的事   是幫忙尋找長岡先生他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,還有想向誰傳達什麼   對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,要放棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要放棄   我有話必須告訴她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.18,0:06:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,只是還來不及和她說明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:18.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,不惜使用 Hand Shakers 的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,即便這能力如此特別
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就算遙不願意   我也絕對會見到她
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.61,0:06:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可能會給爸爸添麻煩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.08,0:06:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼   一起去不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你的能力   或許我也能使用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,由於自己的任性而帶給手綱不必要的麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.40,0:06:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你一定有這樣的顧慮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,這種時候只得依賴父母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.76,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.76,0:07:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然是個被手綱一擊就打敗的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.85,0:07:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不可靠的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:08.23,Default,,0,0,0,,謝謝您  爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,誰叫我是你的保護者   沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.70,0:07:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,現在可能不適合這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.08,0:07:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,不   現在還是別說了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,欸   不說我反而更在意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.05,0:07:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,可是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.15,0:07:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,說吧   爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.78,0:08:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你其實是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.20,0:08:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,養子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.96,0:08:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡   果然不該現在告訴你才對
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,不過相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,不管你是不是我們的親生兒子…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.52,0:08:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就猜到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.92,0:08:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,綠燈了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,啊  喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會？ 什麼時候知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.42,0:08:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,難道是勝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.68,0:08:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟我從沒看過讀小學以前的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.68,0:08:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直都很不安
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.25,0:08:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,假如不是你們的親生兒子該怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.61,0:08:49.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我到底是來自哪裡的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.92,0:08:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.52,0:08:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但爸爸依然是爸爸這點永遠不變   我是這麼認為的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.48,0:09:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼嘛   突然變得這麼能言善道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,還以為你會哭呢   可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,男人就是這樣慢慢的堅強起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.85,0:09:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,可是我覺得現在能說出來真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.68,0:09:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.40,0:09:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那就是宿舍嗎   太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.91,0:09:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸   差不多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.78,0:09:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯   我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,前往「通靈塔」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.91,0:09:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(1011.734,976.8)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,「通靈塔」…真令人懷念
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.12,0:09:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(786.134,976.8)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,真的假的   這就是你的能力嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.34,0:09:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡搭車還是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.22,0:09:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,按照計劃   接下來只要抵達小遙的房間就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.44,0:09:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,不過這真是不得了的能力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,想做什麼都可以
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我才不想做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.06,0:09:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我明白   你只想見見小遙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.49,0:10:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,快跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,你在開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,遙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.08,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是護衛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,初次見面   荒城令次郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我是隸屬奧池翠少爺的執事   名為斯蒂安 ·  瀨馬
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.36,0:10:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那名字是假名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.00,0:10:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,翠少爺賜予給我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,便是我目前的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,翠先生不在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼這就是遙的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.42,0:11:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,遙果真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.16,0:11:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,麻煩兩位請回吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.05,0:11:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,遙   和我一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧   幸也和叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.63,0:11:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,絕對不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,兩位這是不願回去的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊   不會走的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.84,0:11:34.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不想走的話   你想怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,恕我冒犯   我將會對兩位使用「寧錄」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1341.733,979.733)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是嗎   混帳傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,擊潰你的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Break  Chain
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,請容我介紹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Requie  Noble
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.67,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你快走
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,別過來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,遙的「寧錄」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(1018,981.333)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.72,0:13:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Disc
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.24,0:13:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.54,0:13:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你不只是單純的執事或護衛而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你的手段過於粗暴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,如今的我   只是一名執事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.12,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,與您相比   至少強了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.81,0:13:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,作為一個 Hand Shakers 也比全盛時期的你更強
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.20,0:13:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,這並不是自傲
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,沒有「賓得」陪伴的你   是不可能有勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.14,0:14:00.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs48\pos(636.8,983)}Bind
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯   確實是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.32,0:14:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,不過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,這次我有不能輸的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.08,0:14:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只能徹底斬殺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.40,0:14:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,放馬過來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.19,0:14:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,竟然利用鎖鏈當鎧甲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.91,0:14:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,選擇捨身嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你的確比我強
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.70,0:14:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,但是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我的鎖鏈卻讓你無法動彈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,不知何時成長為男子漢的兒子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.41,0:14:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,在那樣的兒子面前怎麼能輸給你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.75,0:14:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,老實做我的獵物吧   混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.83,0:15:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好了   輪到你了   幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,你離開吧   不要看我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,我不走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.18,0:15:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,你回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.73,0:15:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.90,0:15:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,為了文化祭那時的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經失去資格了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.46,0:15:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,資格什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.36,0:15:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.62,0:15:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我放棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我無法像幸也這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.08,0:16:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,無法像以前一樣和你說話
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也被說壞話時   我什麼都沒有反駁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.28,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,結果又說謊了   明明我是最了解幸也的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.15,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.75,0:16:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我盡是在說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.61,0:16:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,只有這點事情嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.35,0:16:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,這點…事情？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.29,0:16:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我太差勁了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.58,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,才會想為幸也做些我能辦到的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.05,0:16:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,若是我也有可以做到的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.40,0:16:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,抱…抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.60,0:16:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,然而對我來說這並不是什麼大不了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,對於那樣的說法我早已習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.78,0:17:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,既陰沉又內向   說話還很無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,何況我也是最了解遙的人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.60,0:17:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我也對妳說了謊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.45,0:17:16.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我希望遙哪裡都別去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.38,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我的搭檔絕對只有遙一人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.32,0:17:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,不是搭檔也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.24,0:17:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.66,0:17:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,遙總是陪伴在我身邊鼓勵著我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,妳的笑容會使我變得有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,覺得可以繼續待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.83,0:17:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我不要再對妳說謊了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.21,0:17:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,所以說…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.07,0:17:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡遙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是有幸也在身旁才能露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,文化祭也是看見了幸也努力才變得積極的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.54,0:18:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜歡幸也
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.31,0:18:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因為喜歡…而滿嘴謊言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,「通靈塔」的事情我全都記得一清二楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.66,0:18:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\pos(605.334,977.333)}Ziggurat
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.33,0:18:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,卻害怕被你討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我也在說謊喔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.24,0:18:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,明明已經知道了遙還記得這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,妳受傷讓我感到很恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,事實上謊稱妳忘記一切的我也在自欺欺人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.00,0:18:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.35,0:18:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不  還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,沒用的  大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.77,0:18:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,幸也   讓我們一起戰鬥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好的   遙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.32,0:19:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,遙小姐的力量正在消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.92,0:19:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.50,0:19:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,準備開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.28,0:19:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你的「寧錄」應該不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.83,0:19:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs36\pos(869.333,979.333)}Nimrod
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我有說過那種話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.90,0:20:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,打敗他了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.45,0:20:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,大概吧   或許是回到現實了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.44,0:20:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.65,0:20:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,對不起啊   什麼都沒有說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是很對不起   完全沒察覺到妳的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我想傳達給妳我來不及對妳說的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.91,0:20:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯   將那些未完的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,那我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.00,0:21:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法回到現實
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊   少年的常規
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我並不討厭這個預料
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,您是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.44,0:21:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,在這裡擊碎你們
Dialogue: 1,0:21:40.87,0:21:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}隠しているんじゃない
Dialogue: 1,0:21:46.92,0:21:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}大事に護っていたいだけ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:52.96,0:21:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}心にしまいこんだ
Dialogue: 1,0:21:58.90,0:22:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}淡い愛しさを
Dialogue: 1,0:22:04.07,0:22:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}君の願い聞かせてほしい
Dialogue: 1,0:22:10.16,0:22:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}夢の中でいい    寄り添っていたい
Dialogue: 1,0:22:19.14,0:22:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}ねえ　神様はきっと
Dialogue: 1,0:22:25.09,0:22:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}まだ　決めてはいないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:31.12,0:22:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}そう　この出会いが　運命でも　偶然でも　いいの
Dialogue: 1,0:22:43.06,0:22:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}ねえ　二人の間に
Dialogue: 1,0:22:49.16,0:22:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}ほら　不幸などないよ
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.27,0:23:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}そう　迷う日々も　どんなときも
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.68,0:23:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fnConstantia\i0\fs60\c&HEEFEFF&\b1\2c&HEEFEFF&\3c&HEFFBFC&\3a&HDC&\4c&H000000&\4a&HC8&}前を向いてさ　笑っていよう
